[normal]sequence of events.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal](
[normal]i
[normal]) By accident of historical representation, this firm was already
[normal] 
[normal]representing a number of individuals on TPIMs who were
[normal] 
[normal]wearing the new (introduced in or around April 2012) GPS
[normal] 
[normal]satellite tag. A growing number of arrests took place of
[normal] 
[normal]separate individuals, not known to each other all of whom
[normal] 
[normal]expressed astonishment at the allegation by the monitoring
[normal] 
[normal]company G4S, that they had deliberately interfered with their
[normal] 
[normal]tags. (Solicitors representing a further individual reported that a
[normal] 
[normal]similar allegation had been made in his case.)Two reports of
[normal] 
[normal]"tampering" for two separate individuals came when they had
[normal] 
[normal]on separate occasions, in separate cities, been praying in a
[normal] 
[normal]mosque.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal](ii) Over a period of a year, this firm had already expressed clearly
[normal] 
